-- utah-remaining-counties-communities-seed.sql
-- Bucket (b): the 22 remaining Utah counties (all UT counties minus the 7 already live:
-- Box Elder, Cache, Davis, Salt Lake, Tooele, Utah, Weber). Per-ZIP backbone, county
-- government layered via parent_id (docs/community-build-source-of-truth.md §13/§13.9).
-- Pages-only (Phase 1); feeds are Phase 2, county-by-county, after pages confirmed.
-- Source dataset: `zipcodes` PyPI v3.0.0 (bundled offline USPS DB, §12.0) — no ZIP guessed.
-- Collision probe vs live communities.zip_codes: 84536 (Monument Valley, already an AZ
--   zip page under Navajo County) and 84665 (already a UT Utah County zip page 'Lake Shore')
--   were EXCLUDED (no duplicate zip page, kept off the county array) per §9/§12.4.
-- Idempotent: on conflict (slug) do nothing. County slugs carry -ut suffix (§9).

